# Runnable — Implementation Walkthrough

## What Was Built

A complete self-hosted web application for managing server directories and hosting, built from scratch in a monorepo.

---

## Project Structure

```
runnable/
├── package.json                    # npm workspaces root
├── docker-compose.yml              # PostgreSQL + services
├── .env.example                    # All configurable variables
├── .gitignore
├── client/                         # React + TypeScript + Vite
│   ├── vite.config.ts              # Dev proxy to backend
│   └── src/
│       ├── api/                    # Typed API clients
│       │   ├── client.ts           # Axios + auto token refresh
│       │   ├── auth.ts
│       │   └── projects.ts
│       ├── store/                  # Zustand state
│       │   ├── authStore.ts
│       │   └── projectStore.ts
│       ├── pages/
│       │   ├── Login.tsx
│       │   ├── Register.tsx
│       │   ├── AuthCallback.tsx
│       │   ├── Dashboard.tsx       # Project cards + create modal
│       │   ├── ProjectDetail.tsx   # 5-tab detail view
│       │   └── Settings.tsx
│       ├── components/
│       │   ├── Layout.tsx          # Sidebar + header
│       │   ├── StatusBadge.tsx     # Animated status indicators
│       │   ├── FileBrowser.tsx     # Drag-drop file manager
│       │   └── LogViewer.tsx
│       ├── App.tsx                 # Routes + auth guards
│       └── index.css               # Full design system
└── server/                         # Express + TypeScript
    └── src/
        ├── config/                 # Env config + TypeORM DataSource
        ├── entities/               # 5 TypeORM entities
        ├── middleware/             # Auth, errors, uploads
        ├── services/              # 7 service classes
        ├── routes/                # 5 route files
        └── index.ts               # Express + Socket.IO entry
```

---

## Backend

### Entities
| Entity | Purpose |
|--------|---------|
| [User](file:///Users/araasryan/AndroidStudioProjects/runnable/server/src/entities/User.ts) | Auth, roles, OAuth IDs |
| [Project](file:///Users/araasryan/AndroidStudioProjects/runnable/server/src/entities/Project.ts) | Hosted directories with server config |
| [GithubRepo](file:///Users/araasryan/AndroidStudioProjects/runnable/server/src/entities/GithubRepo.ts) | Linked repos with webhook secrets |
| [CustomDomain](file:///Users/araasryan/AndroidStudioProjects/runnable/server/src/entities/CustomDomain.ts) | User-assigned domains with DNS verification |
| [AppSettings](file:///Users/araasryan/AndroidStudioProjects/runnable/server/src/entities/AppSettings.ts) | Global config (upload limits, base domain) |

### Services
| Service | Key Features |
|---------|-------------|
| [AuthService](file:///Users/araasryan/AndroidStudioProjects/runnable/server/src/services/auth.service.ts) | JWT tokens, bcrypt, OAuth user creation |
| [ServerConfigService](file:///Users/araasryan/AndroidStudioProjects/runnable/server/src/services/serverConfig.service.ts) | Generates Caddy/Nginx/Apache configs |
| [ProcessService](file:///Users/araasryan/AndroidStudioProjects/runnable/server/src/services/process.service.ts) | Start/stop/restart + Socket.IO status |
| [GithubService](file:///Users/araasryan/AndroidStudioProjects/runnable/server/src/services/github.service.ts) | Clone, pull, webhooks, auto-deploy |
| [FileManagerService](file:///Users/araasryan/AndroidStudioProjects/runnable/server/src/services/fileManager.service.ts) | Upload/download/delete with path traversal protection |
| [DomainService](file:///Users/araasryan/AndroidStudioProjects/runnable/server/src/services/domain.service.ts) | DNS verification (CNAME/TXT), auto-TLS |
| [SandboxService](file:///Users/araasryan/AndroidStudioProjects/runnable/server/src/services/sandbox.service.ts) | Per-project Unix users, cgroups, command allowlist |

### API Routes
- **Auth**: Register, login, refresh, GitHub/Google OAuth
- **Projects**: CRUD + start/stop/restart + status/logs
- **Files**: List, upload (multipart), download, delete, mkdir
- **GitHub**: Connect repo, disconnect, webhook receiver
- **Domains**: Add, verify DNS, remove

